A requirement for minikube is docker, howerver there may be some issues with docker
* If there are issues with docker run the following commands:
    sudo service docker restart  -  Restarts Docker


* install kubectl as well: This allows user interaction with kubernetes clusters.
https://kubernetes.io/docs/tasks/tools/install-kubectl-linux/ 

* Error 1
If error message "unit is masked"
Docker, unit is masked: follow instructions here: https://forums.docker.com/t/failed-to-start-docker-service-unit-is-masked/67413/1
 
* Error 2
if errors still occur, install docker from the main website
FOLLOW THIS DOCKER INSTALL GUIDE HERE:
https://docs.docker.com/engine/install/ubuntu/

* Error 3
Docker dead, daemon inactive, solution
https://serverfault.com/questions/1155735/docker-daemon-inactive-dead  
